WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=LOCAL:00:00:00.000,MPEGTS:0

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.000
♪ You're the only one in my heart ♪

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.079
♪ Even if you never know ♪

00:00:16.079 --> 00:00:19.880
♪ I'll keep watching over you ♪

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:23.600
♪ I love you more than words
but our path isn't easy ♪

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.120
♪ I just need you to believe in me ♪

00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:30.800
♪ I'm weak for your lips ♪

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:34.760
♪ And the kiss upon my forehead ♪

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:41.560
♪ Every action conveys these words, you know? ♪

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:45.000
♪ Can you hear me saying I love you? ♪

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.040
♪ Use the feeling you know ♪

00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:51.200
♪ And you'll love so deeply ♪

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:55.160
♪ Can you feel my love? ♪

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:59.840
♪ Please know that I love you ♪

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:02.040
I'm happy to see you again.

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:04.519
Maylin is the daughter of my mom's best friend.

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:07.080
But it doesn't seem that way with your mom.

00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:08.800
Can I be direct with you?

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:10.800
You like Runch, don't you?

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.200
Auntie!

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.320
Let's stay like this. It's nice.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.280
I hope your plan works, Mom.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:18.840
It's really a shooting--

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.640
What are you looking at, Runch?

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:38.960
Just making sure that this isn't a dream.

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:44.680
Waking up to see your face like this…

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:47.080
makes me so happy.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:54.200
So cheesy in the morning. You're making me blush.

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.920
You also blushed last night.

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:07.360
And the night before.

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:10.759
And the night before that too.

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:12.720
Stop it.

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:18.880
If you sleep somewhere else again,
I won't have it.

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:23.400
I don't want to sleep anywhere else either

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:26.640
if it's not next to you like this.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:31.200
My beautiful girl.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.200
I love it when you call me yours.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:38.880
Like what?

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:42.320
Like…

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:45.960
"My wife."

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:48.480
"My spouse."

00:02:49.480 --> 00:02:51.120
Or "My girl."

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:56.280
You're melting my heart.

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.320
My wife.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:04.040
My spouse.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.920
You are my girl.

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.200
So…

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.280
Can I be yours forever?

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:27.880
I wouldn't let you belong to anyone else.

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.400
Yes, Mr. Aphichet?

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.320
I will.

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:48.520
Ms. Runch, please take a seat.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:49.520
Sure.

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:57.040
Maylin?

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.440
Runch.

00:04:59.640 --> 00:05:01.560
You two know each other?

00:05:01.760 --> 00:05:03.800
Yes, we do.

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:05.320
That's perfect.

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:08.600
Maylin's academic advisor
happens to be my best friend,

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:12.280
so he asked me to hire his star student.

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:15.320
I noticed that your team is still shorthanded,

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:18.960
so I decided to place her into your team.

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:20.720
I'd be glad to.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:23.640
I will take the absolute best care of her.

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:25.720
Thank you, Runch.

00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:28.720
I've always wanted to work with you.

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:33.560
In that case, you can go ahead
and get her oriented.

00:05:33.800 --> 00:05:34.600
Will do.

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:52.760
Everyone,

00:05:54.280 --> 00:05:56.840
this is Maylin, the newest member of our team.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.200
Please look after her.

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:00.880
Hi, everyone.

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:03.600
I'm Maylin. It's an honor to be here.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.680
Over here.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:16.680
You can take this desk.

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:21.400
If you have any questions,
ask me anytime, don't be shy.

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:22.640
I will, Runch.

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:28.760
I'll have you look over the case files
we're currently working on, okay?

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:30.000
Sure.

00:06:30.320 --> 00:06:32.040
-Take it easy.
-Thank you.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:43.240
Welcome to the team, Maylin.

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:44.560
I'm Utt.

00:06:46.640 --> 00:06:48.680
Hello, I'm Maylin.

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:54.600
So, you and Runch already knew each other?

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:57.680
Yes, we go way back.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:00.040
Since we were kids.

00:07:52.200 --> 00:07:53.160
Neen?

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:57.600
You're back?

00:07:59.320 --> 00:08:02.520
I put together a little something for you.

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:09.800
You did this for me?

00:08:10.080 --> 00:08:10.960
Yeah.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:13.200
You always look exhausted after work,

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:15.640
so I wanted to cheer you up.

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:21.120
If it's not pretty or not to your liking,
please don't hold it against me.

00:08:22.760 --> 00:08:24.040
It's beautiful.

00:08:25.400 --> 00:08:28.840
I love everything that you do for me.

00:08:53.840 --> 00:08:55.800
I have a favor to ask you.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:58.200
What is it?

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.560
I bought a new outfit.

00:09:07.520 --> 00:09:09.600
I want to wear it for you tonight.

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:15.000
But I'd look even prettier
if you put it on me yourself.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:18.680
Will you do it?

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:20.480
I'd love to.

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.040
But…

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:43.600
But I think…

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:49.040
you'd look even prettier
if you wore nothing at all.

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:25.680
The core of this case boils down to intent.

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:29.400
That's why you need to go through
the timeline carefully.

00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:31.840
I will, Runch.

00:10:35.640 --> 00:10:36.920
And also,

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:40.760
try opening this file.

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:44.360
-This one?
-Yes.

00:10:59.080 --> 00:11:00.000
See?

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:01.800
I told you guys.

00:11:02.640 --> 00:11:05.080
Those two must have something going on.

00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:08.960
Why get so close just to look at some documents?

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:09.760
Yeah.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:11.200
That's not normal.

00:11:11.400 --> 00:11:12.760
Yeah, anyone can tell.

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:15.440
The new girl is totally infatuated.

00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:16.920
And Runch's so handsome.

00:11:16.920 --> 00:11:18.640
No wonder she's into her.

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:21.000
Trust me,

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:24.320
there is definitely something between those two.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:31.200
Hey, give that back. I'll be right back.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:32.680
Ms. Neen?

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.440
-Are you here to see my boss?
-Yes.

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:39.400
Oh, you didn't call her first?

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:41.640
She just left with the new girl.

00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:44.600
The new girl?

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:46.280
Yes.

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:50.240
Well, I don't know if I should say this.

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:52.680
I don't want you to misunderstand.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.560
Go ahead. I'm listening.

00:11:56.560 --> 00:12:00.680
Well, lately, Runch and the new hire,

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:04.360
Maylin, have been working on
a project together every day.

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:09.640
Working together every day is normal, isn't it?

00:12:10.400 --> 00:12:11.600
It is,

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:16.000
but I think those two are…

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:18.240
closer than they should be.

00:12:19.160 --> 00:12:21.720
I found out they already knew each other.

00:12:21.880 --> 00:12:23.720
Since they were kids apparently.

00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:29.200
I don't want you two to fight,

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:31.960
but this picture…

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:34.120
says something.

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:50.240
It's probably just the new project.

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:53.040
Runch's always serious about her work.

00:12:53.800 --> 00:12:56.560
Yes, I hope that's the case.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.280
Excuse me, Ms. Neen.

00:13:13.400 --> 00:13:16.200
Lately, Runch and the new hire,

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:19.480
Maylin, have been working on
a project together every day.

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:23.280
Those two are closer than they should be.

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:26.080
This picture says something.

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:39.520
I'm sorry.

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:46.000
I'm sorry for being late.

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:49.320
The client just wouldn't stop talking.

00:13:50.760 --> 00:13:53.920
It's okay, you're usually busy with work anyway.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:57.440
I missed you all day.

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:05.080
How was work at the office?

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:10.520
We're currently laying out the case,
so it's quite a lot of work.

00:14:15.560 --> 00:14:17.680
So many projects.

00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:20.080
Has your team gotten more people?

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:23.440
One person just joined,

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:25.160
but she's still new,

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:27.880
so I need to work closely with her.

00:14:31.280 --> 00:14:33.560
And who is she and where's she from?

00:14:34.280 --> 00:14:35.840
She's hired by Mr. Aphichet.

00:14:38.760 --> 00:14:41.240
Someone recommended her for the job.

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:45.240
Once she's settled in,
we'll be able to divide the work,

00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:48.560
but for now, we have to work together.

00:14:51.280 --> 00:14:55.000
Runch, so are you close with her?

00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:57.440
No.

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:02.320
We're just colleagues.

00:15:13.640 --> 00:15:16.640
Lately, Runch and the new hire,

00:15:16.960 --> 00:15:20.200
Maylin, have been working on
a project together every day.

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:23.880
Those two are closer than they should be.

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.720
Ugh, why can't I stop thinking about this?

00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:29.360
Ms. Neen?

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:31.160
Are you okay?

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:38.960
I'm fine. I just have something on my mind.

00:15:47.160 --> 00:15:50.520
Nut, I have to take care of something today,
so I won't be back.

00:15:50.520 --> 00:15:52.280
Call me if you need anything.

00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:00.840
Sure, sounds good.

00:16:04.280 --> 00:16:05.160
Ms. Neen?

00:16:05.360 --> 00:16:06.280
Hello.

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:07.200
Hello.

00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:11.600
Is Runch here?

00:16:15.760 --> 00:16:19.120
We need to go over this testimony again.

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:22.560
Then compare it with the opposition's timeline.

00:16:22.840 --> 00:16:26.680
If we don't get the details right,
we'll get destroyed on cross.

00:16:31.880 --> 00:16:33.000
Maylin.

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:34.840
Are you okay?

00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:37.960
Oh.

00:16:38.320 --> 00:16:42.720
I'm fine. I just feel a little dizzy.

00:16:44.200 --> 00:16:46.200
Did you get enough sleep last night?

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:50.320
Last night, I got only two hours of sleep.

00:16:51.000 --> 00:16:53.720
I stayed up preparing the brief for you.

00:16:54.480 --> 00:16:56.360
Two hours isn't enough.

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:02.120
In our line of work, focus is everything.

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:06.000
If your body isn't up for it,
your brain won't be either.

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.520
I just wanted to do a good job.

00:17:11.480 --> 00:17:13.319
I don't want to disappoint you.

00:17:14.640 --> 00:17:17.839
Get some rest and feel better.
We can do this later.

00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:20.079
I will.

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:27.880
Oh, Maylin?

00:17:28.119 --> 00:17:29.120
Boss?

00:17:34.360 --> 00:17:35.360
Neen?

00:17:39.240 --> 00:17:40.720
I'm so sorry, boss.

00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:43.800
Ms. Neen was looking for you,
so I brought her here.

00:17:44.120 --> 00:17:47.080
I didn't think that you and Maylin would be…

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:50.920
Neen.

00:17:57.880 --> 00:17:58.720
Sit down.

00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:00.920
Sit here.

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:04.040
Neen!

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:12.280
Mr. Utt?

00:18:13.320 --> 00:18:16.040
Who was that woman?

00:18:19.280 --> 00:18:20.600
She's Runch's wife.

00:18:27.840 --> 00:18:28.800
Neen!

00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:34.840
Neen, hear me out. It's not what you're thinking.

00:18:39.640 --> 00:18:42.280
Maylin felt dizzy and was about to faint,

00:18:42.600 --> 00:18:44.680
so I was just steadying her.

00:18:45.280 --> 00:18:47.040
There is nothing more to it.

00:18:48.560 --> 00:18:50.120
I'll believe you on this,

00:18:50.840 --> 00:18:52.400
but there's another thing.

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:55.960
Utt said you've known
that woman since you were kids.

00:18:56.320 --> 00:18:57.560
Is that true?

00:19:04.760 --> 00:19:06.680
I was afraid it would upset you.

00:19:07.240 --> 00:19:11.000
I didn't want you to worry, so I didn't tell you.

00:19:17.720 --> 00:19:21.400
So you've already decided
what I should and shouldn't know

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:23.320
without even asking me.

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:31.160
I've always trusted you.

00:19:33.040 --> 00:19:35.200
But today, you made me feel like

00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:38.440
there's a whole side of you I don't even know.

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:42.880
Who knows what else you're hiding from me.

00:19:46.320 --> 00:19:48.760
Is there anything else you haven't told me?

00:19:51.560 --> 00:19:52.640
No.

00:19:53.240 --> 00:19:54.440
Nothing else.

00:19:55.240 --> 00:19:57.240
And I won't let this happen again.

00:19:57.920 --> 00:20:00.200
I won't hide anything from you again.

00:20:00.760 --> 00:20:01.960
I promise.

00:20:29.040 --> 00:20:30.160
Maylin?

00:20:31.360 --> 00:20:35.080
Are you free this evening?
Why don't you come over for dinner?

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:38.640
Oh, you want to talk to me too?

00:20:39.240 --> 00:20:41.760
That's perfect. See you this evening.

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:43.440
Goodbye.

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:47.720
I'm warning you. I'm warning you.

00:20:49.200 --> 00:20:50.160
What's that?

00:20:50.800 --> 00:20:52.920
I was talking to a mosquito, not you.

00:20:52.960 --> 00:20:56.720
I'm warning you.
Don't you dare bite me. I'll swat you dead.

00:20:56.720 --> 00:21:00.240
Who even talks to mosquitoes?
You're losing it more every day.

00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:02.040
I'm going out for groceries.

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:06.440
You wanna die? Don't bite me. I'm warning you.

00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:08.600
I'm only tough on mosquitoes.

00:21:11.800 --> 00:21:12.840
Eat more.

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:17.200
You too, you need to eat more as well.

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:19.520
You've gotten too thin lately.

00:21:21.760 --> 00:21:23.200
You've gotten thin too.

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:26.960
Still love me like this?

00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:30.040
Of course I do.

00:21:31.200 --> 00:21:34.360
I love you even more. I love you more every day.

00:21:45.960 --> 00:21:46.880
Yes, Mom?

00:21:49.840 --> 00:21:50.760
What?

00:21:51.720 --> 00:21:53.000
You're feeling sick?

00:21:59.320 --> 00:22:01.600
Okay, I'll head over there now.

00:22:02.080 --> 00:22:02.880
Okay.

00:22:07.600 --> 00:22:09.600
-Neen, I have to…
-Get the bill.

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:11.440
I'm coming with you.

00:22:18.040 --> 00:22:20.560
Runch is on her way. Let's wait for her.

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:27.800
Actually, I don't think
I can have dinner with you today.

00:22:28.360 --> 00:22:29.800
What? Why is that?

00:22:34.080 --> 00:22:36.640
There's something I want to ask you.

00:22:39.520 --> 00:22:41.160
Is Runch married?

00:22:46.760 --> 00:22:47.720
Yes.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:51.000
Uh, hear me out.

00:22:51.000 --> 00:22:54.600
They've been having problems.
They're close to getting divorced.

00:22:54.680 --> 00:22:56.680
Hey, how could you say that?

00:22:56.680 --> 00:22:59.240
I'm telling the truth. Why would I hide it?

00:23:01.360 --> 00:23:03.800
I'm so sorry I didn't tell you.

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:07.040
I thought they would be divorced soon,

00:23:07.320 --> 00:23:09.240
so I chose not to say anything.

00:23:09.640 --> 00:23:12.640
Did someone say anything about a divorce, Mother?

00:23:17.480 --> 00:23:18.720
Why are you here?

00:23:18.720 --> 00:23:20.800
Don't ask her that. It's rude.

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.520
Maylin is the daughter of my best friend.

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:25.680
She's here because I invited her,

00:23:25.680 --> 00:23:30.000
unlike some people who weren't invited
but still have the nerve to show up.

00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:33.920
The way you're talking,
you don't seem sick at all.

00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:35.560
You're so fake.

00:23:35.560 --> 00:23:38.840
Hey, you little brat! Are you calling me a liar?

00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:41.200
Glad you get it, so I don't have to repeat myself!

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:42.680
Stop it, Neen.

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:45.880
Tell your mother to stop first, and I'll stop.

00:23:46.720 --> 00:23:49.280
Maylin, I'm so sorry

00:23:49.280 --> 00:23:51.440
you had to come here and see all this.

00:23:51.520 --> 00:23:53.920
I think I'd better go.

00:23:53.920 --> 00:23:55.640
Wait, you haven't eaten yet.

00:23:55.640 --> 00:23:57.080
Maybe next time, Auntie.

00:23:58.040 --> 00:23:59.480
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

00:23:59.960 --> 00:24:00.840
Maylin.

00:24:05.320 --> 00:24:07.920
You little brat. You ruined everything!

00:24:07.920 --> 00:24:09.360
It's you who did that.

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:12.280
What were you thinking, bringing that woman here?

00:24:12.280 --> 00:24:14.440
And telling her we're getting a divorce?

00:24:14.440 --> 00:24:16.920
What now? Are you trying to find Runch a mistress?

00:24:16.920 --> 00:24:19.720
What mistress? Don't you dare insult Maylin.

00:24:19.720 --> 00:24:21.720
Insult her? I'm telling the truth.

00:24:21.920 --> 00:24:26.040
She's involved with a married person.
What should I call her if not a mistress?

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:27.520
-A lover?
-You!

00:24:28.040 --> 00:24:28.920
You crazy minx!

00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:33.200
Runch, let's go home. We need to talk.

00:24:34.840 --> 00:24:35.800
Runch.

00:24:36.040 --> 00:24:38.000
Runch, don't go.

00:24:38.200 --> 00:24:39.560
Runch, wait.

00:24:39.840 --> 00:24:40.640
Hey.

00:24:40.840 --> 00:24:41.720
Runch!

00:24:41.760 --> 00:24:42.560
Runch!

00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:47.280
Honey…

00:24:55.040 --> 00:24:59.520
I know it's all my fault for not telling you
about my mom knowing Maylin.

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:01.280
So you know.

00:25:02.520 --> 00:25:06.560
Even after I asked you
if you were hiding anything from me,

00:25:06.840 --> 00:25:07.960
you said no.

00:25:08.400 --> 00:25:10.200
And you even promised me.

00:25:10.280 --> 00:25:12.440
It hasn't even been a full day, Runch.

00:25:15.520 --> 00:25:17.520
I have no excuse.

00:25:20.520 --> 00:25:22.640
But the reason I didn't tell you

00:25:23.400 --> 00:25:25.560
is because I didn't want you to worry,

00:25:25.720 --> 00:25:27.720
and I don't have feelings for her.

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:29.080
But she does.

00:25:30.760 --> 00:25:34.680
She knows I'm married,
so I don't think she sees me that way.

00:25:36.080 --> 00:25:39.640
So what? She clearly has your mother's support.

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:41.320
How could she not want you?

00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:43.320
My mom would never do that.

00:25:43.320 --> 00:25:44.400
Give me a break.

00:25:46.240 --> 00:25:49.240
Your mother told that woman
we were getting a divorce,

00:25:49.240 --> 00:25:50.200
even though…

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:58.480
Even though we're really doing that.

00:26:00.480 --> 00:26:02.080
But your mother didn't know that.

00:26:02.720 --> 00:26:05.840
That means she lied to that woman

00:26:05.840 --> 00:26:08.560
because she was dying to have me replaced.

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:11.000
No one can replace you, Neen.

00:26:24.560 --> 00:26:26.520
I will never love anyone else.

00:26:29.880 --> 00:26:31.280
What I did,

00:26:32.280 --> 00:26:34.040
I did to protect you.

00:26:35.480 --> 00:26:38.520
This isn't what people in love do
to protect each other.

00:26:40.080 --> 00:26:41.560
So what do I have to do?

00:26:42.400 --> 00:26:46.080
What do I have to do to convince you
I really want to protect you?

00:26:47.520 --> 00:26:48.480
I don't know.

00:26:50.320 --> 00:26:52.160
I guess you'll have to show me.

00:26:55.840 --> 00:26:57.880
Let's sleep in separate rooms tonight.

00:27:00.200 --> 00:27:01.120
Neen.

00:27:12.480 --> 00:27:15.040
Breakfast with a crispy fried egg for you.

00:28:02.280 --> 00:28:05.400
Maylin isn't picking up my calls
or reading my messages.

00:28:05.400 --> 00:28:06.880
She must be mad at me.

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:11.840
Did you hear what I said?

00:28:12.360 --> 00:28:14.400
What? I'm watching the news.

00:28:14.400 --> 00:28:16.280
You're not listening to me at all.

00:28:16.720 --> 00:28:20.680
I am. I heard you, I'm not deaf.
I just don't feel like talking.

00:28:21.280 --> 00:28:22.600
You don't listen to me.

00:28:23.400 --> 00:28:25.480
What are you going to say? Go ahead.

00:28:25.960 --> 00:28:28.280
You're meddling in our daughter's life.

00:28:28.880 --> 00:28:30.200
Stay out of it for once.

00:28:31.480 --> 00:28:34.480
And did Maylin even know
what you were trying to do?

00:28:35.880 --> 00:28:38.560
Are you saying this because you want to stop me?

00:28:38.920 --> 00:28:41.640
This is exactly why I didn't want to talk to you.

00:28:42.080 --> 00:28:43.000
Hey, wait.

00:28:43.600 --> 00:28:45.200
I haven't done anything wrong.

00:28:45.360 --> 00:28:49.880
You saw for yourself.
Maylin is so much nicer than your daughter-in-law.

00:28:50.080 --> 00:28:52.480
Wouldn't you want a daughter-in-law like her?

00:28:52.880 --> 00:28:54.280
Are you out of your mind?

00:28:55.720 --> 00:28:57.880
Runch and Neen are married.

00:28:57.880 --> 00:28:59.560
They registered their marriage.

00:28:59.720 --> 00:29:01.000
Why are you doing this?

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:02.280
They can get a divorce.

00:29:02.760 --> 00:29:05.040
Soon they won't be able to stand each other.

00:29:05.200 --> 00:29:08.160
That's why you keep
stirring things up between them.

00:29:08.400 --> 00:29:11.840
I can't believe you want to win so badly

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:14.320
that you don't even care
about our daughter's feelings.

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:17.800
Trust me, divorcing that rich girl
would be the best thing for Runch.

00:29:17.800 --> 00:29:21.760
If she gets divorced and remarries,
her life will definitely get better.

00:29:23.240 --> 00:29:24.200
Whose life really?

00:29:24.520 --> 00:29:25.440
Hers or yours?

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:27.280
Everything I do, I do for her.

00:29:27.280 --> 00:29:30.520
Can't you see how much Runch's wife outshines her?

00:29:32.240 --> 00:29:36.680
I want people to admire Runch
because she succeeds on her own,

00:29:36.680 --> 00:29:38.200
not because of someone else.

00:29:39.520 --> 00:29:44.240
If she can't live with it, if she can't accept it,
then she has to decide for herself.

00:29:44.280 --> 00:29:45.960
Why do you have to interfere?

00:29:47.240 --> 00:29:49.720
Because I can't stand seeing her belittled.

00:29:49.760 --> 00:29:52.160
Besides, I hate that girl.

00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:56.440
I've been warning you, Ging.

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:58.200
Runch doesn't complain.

00:29:58.640 --> 00:30:00.400
She puts up with everything.

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:03.200
But one day, if she runs out of patience,

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:04.680
I can guarantee

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:08.960
she'll leave for good
and you'll never see her again.

00:30:09.040 --> 00:30:09.960
No way.

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:13.680
I raised her. I know exactly what she's like.

00:30:15.200 --> 00:30:18.800
Someday, you will regret
treating our daughter's family like this.

00:30:32.120 --> 00:30:33.920
What are you looking at, honey?

00:30:33.920 --> 00:30:34.840
Here.

00:30:35.440 --> 00:30:38.000
These photos of Neen and Runch. Look.

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:41.240
Since they got back from the country house,
they started going everywhere together every day.

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:43.880
They even post pictures every day.

00:30:43.920 --> 00:30:47.480
Oh, I'm so happy to see them like this.

00:30:48.120 --> 00:30:49.320
Look at them.

00:30:49.640 --> 00:30:52.800
Oh, Neen. Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

00:30:54.640 --> 00:30:55.880
Are you here alone?

00:30:56.280 --> 00:30:57.320
Where's Runch?

00:30:59.040 --> 00:30:59.680
Don't know.

00:30:59.920 --> 00:31:00.960
-Oh?
-Oh?

00:31:04.120 --> 00:31:05.240
Sulking again?

00:31:06.480 --> 00:31:10.720
Mom was just thrilled to see you
and your wife so in love.

00:31:11.520 --> 00:31:13.760
Can we not? It's pissing me off.

00:31:14.920 --> 00:31:15.840
Did you fight?

00:31:17.360 --> 00:31:18.800
So what do I do then?

00:31:19.240 --> 00:31:20.360
What do you mean?

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:25.400
You really don't remember? Seriously?

00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:33.920
Oh no, I completely forgot!

00:31:35.760 --> 00:31:38.320
Now what are we going to do?

00:31:51.760 --> 00:31:53.760
Is there something you need, Neen?

00:32:01.920 --> 00:32:06.200
Meet me in the fitting room tomorrow at 3 pm.

00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:09.000
We have a company party later that night.

00:32:09.040 --> 00:32:09.880
That's all.

00:32:14.320 --> 00:32:15.960
What's the hurry?

00:32:18.480 --> 00:32:20.800
Don't you want to talk for a bit?

00:32:23.720 --> 00:32:24.520
Nope.

00:32:56.840 --> 00:33:01.080
I tried so hard, and she still wouldn't give in?

00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:51.600
("Earn M Points." Simply scan your receipt
or provide your M Card number.")

00:34:00.560 --> 00:34:01.760
Hello, miss.

00:34:01.760 --> 00:34:02.720
Hello.

00:34:13.120 --> 00:34:13.920
This one.

00:34:14.239 --> 00:34:16.239
Certainly, please follow me.

00:34:24.960 --> 00:34:26.400
Can I collect M Points?

00:34:26.400 --> 00:34:28.000
Yes, you can.

00:34:28.080 --> 00:34:31.719
May I have the phone number
registered with your M Card, please?

00:34:31.719 --> 00:34:32.679
Sure.

00:34:33.239 --> 00:34:34.560
Ms. Runchlaphat?

00:34:34.560 --> 00:34:35.520
Yes.

00:34:35.639 --> 00:34:39.520
Would you like to use your M Points
for an additional 12.5% discount?

00:34:39.520 --> 00:34:41.000
You can redeem it here.

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:41.880
Yes, please.

00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:42.760
Okay.

00:34:44.520 --> 00:34:49.560
The original price is 5,600 baht.
After the discount, the total is 4,900 baht.

00:34:50.159 --> 00:34:51.440
That's quite a discount.

00:34:51.440 --> 00:34:54.639
Yes, it is. Would you like anything else?

00:34:56.560 --> 00:34:57.720
No, that's all.

00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:59.440
Okay, one moment please.

00:34:59.440 --> 00:35:01.320
-Sure.
-How would you like to pay?

00:35:01.560 --> 00:35:02.720
QR code payment, please.

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:03.760
Certainly.

00:35:07.840 --> 00:35:10.440
You look good in everything, Ms. Runch.

00:35:10.600 --> 00:35:11.600
Thank you.

00:35:17.680 --> 00:35:19.560
Ms. Peeracha is ready.

00:35:30.200 --> 00:35:31.360
Neen…

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:33.160
This dress is…

00:35:33.400 --> 00:35:34.720
Beautiful, right?

00:35:37.640 --> 00:35:39.560
It is beautiful, but…

00:35:40.880 --> 00:35:42.240
It's backless.

00:35:44.040 --> 00:35:46.040
I chose it because it's backless.

00:35:47.360 --> 00:35:50.400
You said it yourself
I look beautiful in everything.

00:35:50.640 --> 00:35:52.920
So I must look beautiful in this too.

00:35:58.120 --> 00:36:01.040
I meant something more modest.

00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:05.600
If you wear this to the party,
everyone will be staring at you.

00:36:05.960 --> 00:36:08.560
Oh, so if people stare, you'll be jealous?

00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:13.680
Neen, you're killing me.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:18.000
Okay, I'll take this one.

00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:19.240
Of course.

00:36:21.520 --> 00:36:22.600
Neen…

00:36:32.800 --> 00:36:35.840
Why aren't Neen and Runch here yet?

00:36:40.520 --> 00:36:41.480
There they are.

00:36:49.080 --> 00:36:50.800
Why are you so late?

00:36:51.080 --> 00:36:52.640
Traffic was bad, Mom.

00:36:54.720 --> 00:36:55.600
Neen.

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:00.680
-Geez.
-What?

00:37:01.280 --> 00:37:03.720
Don't you think it's a bit much?

00:37:03.720 --> 00:37:06.360
This is nothing, Nai. I look fabulous.

00:37:07.040 --> 00:37:08.040
Ow!

00:37:08.760 --> 00:37:10.240
Don't pinch me. It hurts.

00:37:11.760 --> 00:37:12.800
I'm sorry.

00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:14.480
I'm just…

00:37:25.280 --> 00:37:26.320
Are you jealous?

00:37:30.880 --> 00:37:34.760
Excuse me, have you forgotten
that you aren't alone here?

00:37:37.600 --> 00:37:40.400
Come on. Let's go to our table. Okay?

00:37:40.400 --> 00:37:41.280
Of course.

00:37:41.720 --> 00:37:42.520
Let's go.

00:37:43.440 --> 00:37:44.400
That one here.

00:37:50.200 --> 00:37:51.760
You don't think it's too much?

00:38:03.920 --> 00:38:06.160
My hip.

00:38:08.240 --> 00:38:09.560
My hip.

00:38:17.680 --> 00:38:20.480
And Pong isn't even home.

00:38:22.200 --> 00:38:23.440
What do I do?

00:38:30.880 --> 00:38:33.000
(Mom)

00:38:35.120 --> 00:38:37.160
(Mom)

00:38:39.640 --> 00:38:40.960
Maybe she's sick again.

00:38:44.000 --> 00:38:44.800
(Mom)

00:38:45.480 --> 00:38:46.480
(March 22, 10.33 pm)

00:38:48.640 --> 00:38:50.760
Why isn't Runch answering me?

00:38:54.520 --> 00:38:55.720
Neen, dear.

00:38:56.680 --> 00:38:58.720
Would you like to dance with me?

00:39:56.760 --> 00:39:58.880
Are you still mad at me, Neen?

00:39:59.560 --> 00:40:00.560
Yes.

00:40:02.560 --> 00:40:04.400
So when will you stop being mad?

00:40:06.640 --> 00:40:09.320
I don't know, I'll see how you behave first.

00:40:11.880 --> 00:40:15.320
It seems you won't forgive me easily this time.

00:40:19.480 --> 00:40:23.560
Every couple has misunderstandings.

00:40:24.800 --> 00:40:29.800
What matters is
whether we're still in this together.

00:40:35.080 --> 00:40:36.960
I'm going to the restroom.

00:40:39.680 --> 00:40:41.000
I'll wait at the table.

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:11.400
(Maylinya)

00:41:15.280 --> 00:41:16.160
Hello?

00:41:18.120 --> 00:41:19.200
What did you say?

00:41:19.840 --> 00:41:21.280
She fell in the bathroom?

00:41:23.680 --> 00:41:25.200
Mom, how are you doing?

00:41:27.640 --> 00:41:29.000
Were you in a lot of pain?

00:41:30.560 --> 00:41:31.600
Of course.

00:41:31.840 --> 00:41:33.120
So much I couldn't get up.

00:41:33.440 --> 00:41:35.480
I almost died in front of the bathroom.

00:41:35.480 --> 00:41:37.680
You wouldn't answer my calls.

00:41:39.160 --> 00:41:42.120
You were too busy partying to care about me.

00:41:42.640 --> 00:41:45.360
Luckily, Maylin came to my rescue.

00:41:45.960 --> 00:41:48.160
Otherwise, I would have died.

00:41:48.560 --> 00:41:50.880
It was just a fall. You weren't gonna die.

00:41:50.880 --> 00:41:53.800
I wasn't talking to you.
I was talking to my daughter.

00:41:54.560 --> 00:41:59.560
If my daughter-in-law were someone else,
she'd have answered my call and rushed over.

00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:02.520
You're the reason Runch turned against me.

00:42:02.520 --> 00:42:03.880
-Hey, I…
-Neen!

00:42:04.680 --> 00:42:05.640
Stop.

00:42:14.920 --> 00:42:15.960
Mom.

00:42:18.120 --> 00:42:21.240
I'm really sorry about what happened today.

00:42:23.320 --> 00:42:26.480
But what you said just now is unfair to Neen.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:34.520
You have no right to set me up with anyone else.

00:42:39.920 --> 00:42:42.840
You have no right
to replace Neen with someone else.

00:42:44.040 --> 00:42:46.640
And you have no right to belittle her.

00:42:47.160 --> 00:42:52.640
You're defending that woman
instead of your own mother?

00:42:52.840 --> 00:42:53.840
Yes, Mom.

00:43:07.720 --> 00:43:09.080
I'm married.

00:43:09.880 --> 00:43:11.840
Neen is my family.

00:43:14.680 --> 00:43:17.000
And you must accept my choice.

00:43:28.600 --> 00:43:29.560
Mom.

00:43:32.360 --> 00:43:35.320
I won't let anyone hurt my wife's feelings.

00:43:36.360 --> 00:43:37.520
No matter who it is.

00:43:38.720 --> 00:43:40.200
Including you, Mom.

00:43:49.120 --> 00:43:50.160
Let's go home.

00:44:53.000 --> 00:44:54.440
Sulking over the rain?

00:44:57.160 --> 00:45:01.120
There goes my sweet beach date
with my beautiful girl.

00:45:03.280 --> 00:45:05.320
I'm sulking over everything right now.

00:45:05.680 --> 00:45:09.040
You look so cute even when you sulk.

00:45:12.400 --> 00:45:16.880
If the rain doesn't stop,
should we stay in our room all day?

00:45:22.040 --> 00:45:23.760
Just staying in the room?

00:45:24.000 --> 00:45:25.840
What are we going to do?

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:34.640
Yeah… what should we do?

00:45:37.120 --> 00:45:38.040
Watch it.

00:45:43.920 --> 00:45:45.080
I've got an idea.

00:45:45.920 --> 00:45:47.680
I know what we should do.

00:45:49.120 --> 00:45:51.280
I promise you won't be bored.

00:45:51.560 --> 00:45:52.760
What's your plan?

00:45:57.520 --> 00:46:00.040
Runch, don't do this.

00:46:00.960 --> 00:46:02.400
I won't be able to stop.

00:46:03.040 --> 00:46:06.440
♪ Can you hear me saying I love you? ♪

00:46:06.720 --> 00:46:08.040
♪ My love is in these soft whispers ♪

00:46:08.040 --> 00:46:09.560
Do we have to stop?

00:46:10.560 --> 00:46:12.880
♪ You have to feel it with your heart ♪

00:46:12.880 --> 00:46:18.040
♪ Our touches will make you understand ♪

00:46:18.040 --> 00:46:21.400
♪ Can you hear me saying I love you? ♪

00:46:21.440 --> 00:46:22.720
I love you.

00:46:25.320 --> 00:46:27.120
I love you too.

00:46:27.560 --> 00:46:31.600
♪ Can you feel my love? ♪

00:46:31.640 --> 00:46:35.000
♪ Please know that I love you ♪

00:46:35.080 --> 00:46:37.400
I want you to split up with that girl.

00:46:37.920 --> 00:46:41.720
If I had known you'd turn out like this
after marrying her,

00:46:42.160 --> 00:46:43.920
I would have stopped it.

00:46:43.920 --> 00:46:46.440
I love Neen. We both love each other.

00:46:46.440 --> 00:46:47.680
But I hate her!

00:46:48.160 --> 00:46:50.160
I want this to be the last time.

00:46:50.760 --> 00:46:52.760
I really want to be happy with you.

00:46:53.040 --> 00:46:55.240
I want to be happy with you too.

00:47:00.240 --> 00:47:03.040
♪ Living with pain and love ♪

00:47:03.040 --> 00:47:05.840
♪ Living while waiting and losing hope ♪

00:47:05.840 --> 00:47:08.280
♪ A voice inside my heart says enough ♪

00:47:08.320 --> 00:47:11.480
♪ But another voice asks me to endure ♪

00:47:11.480 --> 00:47:14.120
♪ I stay because I love you, you know? ♪

00:47:14.120 --> 00:47:19.960
♪ I still believe in the love between us ♪

00:47:20.440 --> 00:47:25.000
♪ Please let us go back to how we were ♪

00:47:25.040 --> 00:47:29.120
♪ I don't know if our love is just impossible ♪

00:47:29.160 --> 00:47:32.000
♪ Or if there's a reason for all of this ♪

00:47:32.000 --> 00:47:36.200
♪ And that reason is you don't love me ♪
